Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.13,0:00:59.14,OP,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.14,0:01:03.96,OP,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.70,0:01:11.78,OP,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:18.93,OP,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.23,0:01:25.55,OP,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.94,0:01:33.21,OP,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.25,0:01:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be dangerous to ignore the enemy base ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.49,0:01:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Chor Tempest will fly reconnaissance in order to locate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.16,0:01:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The {\i1}Messis{\i0} will serve as your relay station.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.80,0:01:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And what should we do when we find the base ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.31,0:02:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If you judge that the circumstances—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.38,0:02:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Under the circumstances, we should completely annihilate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.00,0:02:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you think you were taken off the mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.48,0:02:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.18,0:02:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.46,0:02:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.88,0:02:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something that might be the reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.54,0:02:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.30,0:02:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say. I promised not to. 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.18,0:02:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.79,0:02:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So do I.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.94,0:02:50.60,Series,,0,0,0,,Sibylla
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.72,0:03:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aaeru always does whatever she wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.25,0:03:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, are you sure this is okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.43,0:03:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, I sometimes wonder what those sibyllae are thinking of.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.98,0:03:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,"Really," indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.35,0:03:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If only I could follow my passions as wholeheartedly as she does... 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.78,0:03:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is that Simoun going?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.67,0:03:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.83,0:03:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.88,0:03:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aaeru and Sibylla Yun, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.03,0:03:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Sibylla Aaeru and Sibylla Yun. 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.33,0:03:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Vyura!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.38,0:03:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,After Chor Rubor was dissolved, these two sibyllae were assigned to the {\i1}Messis{\i0} as your replacements.  
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.88,0:04:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They've been conducting reconnaissance missions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.56,0:04:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.98,0:04:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all we can do for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.08,0:04:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard what happened to Dominura and Limone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.46,0:04:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But where are Aaeru and Yun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.81,0:04:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Those two... won't be participating in this mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.42,0:04:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, yes. I'm sure we can discuss the reasons for that later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.00,0:04:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, please, come inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.86,0:04:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll go over the details of the operation...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.59,0:04:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,but first you should get something to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.42,0:04:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's a bit early, but I'm gonna go on ahead, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.80,0:04:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll see you in the dining hall in half an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.24,0:04:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.92,0:04:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be along in a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.58,0:04:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hey, Rodore!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.85,0:04:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.94,0:05:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Mamiina, since you were taking so long...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.91,0:05:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Was I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.26,0:05:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.17,0:05:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Mamiina!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.57,0:05:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Mamiina, your braids are coming undone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.23,0:05:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll fix them for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.80,0:05:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, we do have some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.89,0:05:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if those Simoun from the Ruins made it to the enemy base ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.75,0:05:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.01,0:05:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.54,0:05:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You have Morinas as your pair, and she's an excellent auriga.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.20,0:05:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.62,0:05:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And on top of that, if something goes wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.20,0:05:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be there to protect you, won't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.12,0:05:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.92,0:05:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This is only a reconnaissance mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.89,0:06:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, if we don't fight, nothing bad can happen, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.99,0:06:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.86,0:06:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be best, wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.89,0:06:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,From the information the two of you have gathered,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.09,0:06:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,we've narrowed down the Argentine base ship's area of operations to this region here. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.95,0:06:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,With only those powerless Simile?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.12,0:06:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aurea,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.72,0:06:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the two of us will guard the rear, and relay communications to you. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.73,0:06:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Then—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.69,0:06:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.64,0:06:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll do the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.82,0:06:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The difference in mobility between the Simile and the Simoun is just too great.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.48,0:06:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Creating a mixed unit would be... well, impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.49,0:06:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave it to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.00,0:06:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go again, Floe, making promises you can't keep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.46,0:06:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "again?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.08,0:06:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.77,0:06:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But Alti started—!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.41,0:06:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.07,0:06:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't we all comrades, who have eaten from the same pot?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.66,0:06:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Mamiina, you mustn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.57,0:07:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Uh, nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.28,0:07:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Please continue, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.03,0:07:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.20,0:07:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, first, Chor Tempest...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.91,0:07:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,...should divide into two groups...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.93,0:07:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, Mamiina sure has changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.39,0:07:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.32,0:07:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that "No! You mustn't!" all about, Ro-do-re?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.54,0:07:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Mice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.85,0:07:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.80,0:07:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know that Vyura had been doing recon missions in a Simile.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.99,0:07:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we mustn't waste Vyura and her partner's efforts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.14,0:07:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to stand firm as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.37,0:07:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aurea, we've reached our assigned deployment area.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.14,0:07:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.38,0:07:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The operation will proceed as planned. Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.00,0:07:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.31,0:08:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is Central Command using Chor Tempest this way? 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.55,0:08:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,As Sibylla Dominura correctly pointed out, Central Command doesn't understand a thing! 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.14,0:08:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be quite a while before Chor Tempest returns.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.67,0:08:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This would be a good time for the two of you to get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.28,0:08:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,"Resting is part of duty," huh? 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.74,0:08:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Sibylla.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.07,0:08:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep a sharp eye out for Chor Tempest's return!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.02,0:08:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Set course for the patrol area. All ahead two thirds!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.08,0:08:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.61,0:08:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Mamiina...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.05,0:08:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You were forbidden to attend Angulas's funeral, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.11,0:08:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Our country is really terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.86,0:08:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not so, Sibylla Aurea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.97,0:08:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,As the situation continues to worsen,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.32,0:08:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,people fall back on rules and normality to comfort themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.05,0:09:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.47,0:09:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Mamiina, I believe you've changed. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.37,0:09:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.34,0:09:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.59,0:09:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,She's all "I am going to detach the speaker cable for a while." 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.07,0:09:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That pisses me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.89,0:09:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess they're having an "adult conversation" that they don't want the rest of us to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.80,0:09:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave them alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.83,0:09:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Three o'clock high!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.06,0:09:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a large shadow inside that cloud.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.68,0:09:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.42,0:09:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.98,0:09:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep the speaker cable attached, and approach from above. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.49,0:09:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.42,0:09:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But we found it, so shouldn't we...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.28,0:09:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Those Simoun that we saw at the Ruins could be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.92,0:09:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to find out for certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.14,0:09:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.07,0:09:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's at least confirm that before we head back, Floe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.23,0:09:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.65,0:09:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let down your guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.13,0:10:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This area is likely to be heavily patrolled by the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.08,0:10:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.44,0:10:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,They aren't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.75,0:10:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna leave the patrol area soon, Para-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.30,0:10:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, shouldn't we head back to the rendezvous point with the regina soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.76,0:10:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Para-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.45,0:11:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll search this area for a little while longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.25,0:11:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.43,0:11:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.45,0:11:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the {\i1}Messis{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.16,0:11:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,One Simoun approaching from behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.44,0:11:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Approaching rapidly... It's one of Chor Tempest's Simoun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.08,0:11:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.01,0:11:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Aaeru and Yun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.42,0:11:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Vyura!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.89,0:11:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect to see her on board the {\i1}Messis{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.28,0:11:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's quite a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.17,0:11:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.81,0:11:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I was worried about that as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.45,0:11:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aaeru and Sibylla Yun, please go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.60,0:11:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.31,0:11:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.68,0:11:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.76,0:12:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.69,0:12:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought they'd come.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.80,0:12:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Then?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.60,0:12:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. We'll go too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.02,0:12:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Re-route all power from the helical motors to the engines!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.37,0:12:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Set course for the patrol area. All ahead flank!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.54,0:12:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.08,0:12:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Para-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.10,0:12:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Para-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.25,0:12:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll head to the rendezvous point with the regina.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.84,0:12:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.64,0:12:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.75,0:13:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been spotted!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.99,0:13:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Withdraw at full speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.12,0:13:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Para-sama, behind us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.08,0:13:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Para-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.41,0:13:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd better hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.83,0:13:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.88,0:13:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.14,0:13:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.42,0:13:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Shark Ri Maajon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.73,0:14:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.44,0:14:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Shark Ri Maajon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.09,0:14:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't shake them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.27,0:14:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, they're freakin' quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.45,0:14:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,She...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.56,0:14:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Neviril just told us... to run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.33,0:14:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.73,0:14:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.66,0:14:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to do what Neviril says!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.99,0:14:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, we're both gonna go down!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.36,0:14:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to hurry back and tell the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.49,0:14:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,They're following us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.03,0:14:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand on! We'll be right back, I promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.89,0:15:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aurea!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.47,0:15:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.86,0:15:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aurea...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.37,0:15:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do not worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.75,0:15:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not fail you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.01,0:16:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can understand my words, listen closely!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.34,0:16:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the sort of person to die in a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.67,0:16:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Just another nameless sibylla.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.22,0:16:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care about my own life!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.66,0:16:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But the one who lies behind me is the Simulacrum Theocracy's most revered sibylla, 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.47,0:16:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aurea Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.22,0:16:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,She's going to get out of here safely,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.59,0:16:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and I won't let you lay a finger on her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.34,0:16:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.78,0:16:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,She who is behind you and you who are before me are both glorious sibyllae. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.17,0:16:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The sibyllae of the Holy Land of Simulacrum are the priestesses who dwell closest to God. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.54,0:17:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,In the Plumbum Highlands, we honour you above all others. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.44,0:17:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It is truly regrettable that we must fight you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.17,0:17:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We do not wish to capture an injured sibylla.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.27,0:17:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.07,0:17:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We are priestesses of the Plumbum Highlands.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.86,0:17:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We are nothing like the soldiers from the Archipelago who man this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.55,0:17:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Our recent battle is at an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.74,0:17:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We are no longer called to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.91,0:17:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, you must trust us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.35,0:17:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If our intention was to capture you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.90,0:17:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,there would be no need for such complexity.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.58,0:17:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Mamiina...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.54,0:17:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aurea?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.06,0:17:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Their words... contain no falsehood...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.42,0:18:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.63,0:18:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, do this with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.87,0:18:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.05,0:18:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.32,0:18:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.67,0:18:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If you let us escape from here, you will have nowhere to go back to. 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.69,0:18:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No, if {\i1}you{\i0} are captured, you will be put to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.87,0:19:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You all recognized {\i1}me{\i0} as a true sibylla!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.71,0:19:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If you let me escape, you will all be killed as traitors! 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.19,0:19:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Sibylla Aurea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.76,0:19:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.73,0:19:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather than allow yourself to be murdered by these soldiers, please, allow me...! 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.60,0:19:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the way things should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.27,0:19:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.10,0:20:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,In your language:
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.83,0:20:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Aa-e-ru. 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.58,0:20:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,AA - E - RU ! ! !
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.85,0:20:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Large aircraft, dead ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.52,0:20:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, it must be the Archipelago's base ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.91,0:20:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears to be on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.24,0:20:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,General quarters! All hands, set Condition One throughout the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.86,0:20:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,All hands, set Condition One.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.37,0:20:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.36,0:21:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,All hands, brace for impact! 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.18,0:21:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We will provide support for the priestesses!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.53,0:21:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Mamiina!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.33,0:21:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Quickly! To the {\i1}Messis{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.86,0:21:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.95,0:21:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Noooooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.70,0:21:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Move, Rodoreamon! You're in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.23,0:21:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.32,0:21:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Mamiina!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.78,0:21:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Rodoreamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.94,0:22:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.34,0:22:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Rodoreamon! 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.73,0:22:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to hurry too, Aaeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.99,0:22:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.23,0:22:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to get out of here! We need to escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.03,0:22:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't just stand here doing nothing at a time like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.99,0:22:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Sibylla!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.50,0:22:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sibyllaaaaa!
